ji\" />， 唔好成日諗我可能 失敗咗再諗都未遲 就好似光復香港咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T06:14:15.000Z","msg":"的士佬唔等於佢擁有部的士我咁講你明未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T06:15:39.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 我一早已經講咗 如果啲人冇工開 租唔到佢架車， 佢係咪要食屎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 我唔敢講黃色力量可以幫到幾多的士佬 但而家去搞係一定有啲影響先囉 呢個道理你明唔明啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc79d114f966cf129fec5c70e7bdc422c92f2feb","tid":1921562,"uid":37505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb002ecd1c3c974240c729130a5d968437281025","tid":1921562,"uid":170812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a0c1e5bf974f72b7f52713fb51a1eef626cfa4c","tid":1921562,"uid":199626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7fbe8a09ca183ee963c9dd12c113e9becb8e76f","tid":1921562,"uid":170812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:37:58.000Z","msg":"黃的司機能夠維持生計，當然係好事。<br />\n但司機大部分只係租客。<br />\n的士業界係掌控o係一班的士牌持有人手上。<br />\n即使的士司機汰弱留強最後黃佔大多數，如何向上推一層影響業界，仍然係難嘅。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:45:19.000Z","msg":"你咪叫嗰班業主諗下 係咪想全部的士都冇工開冇人借佢哋牌照囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 好簡單嘅道理 羊毛出自羊身上 到時佢哋一定要跪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T06:00:40.000Z","msg":"個logic係，藍牌主收入來自車租，要攪到佢地，就要影響佢地車租收入。<br />\n<br />\n但唔同罷食、罷買藍店，你罷搭藍的只搭黃的，藍牌主依然有收入；罷搭全部的士，就會攬炒左黃司機。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T06:16:34.000Z","msg":"咁黃店藍業主呢？<br />\n要做係盡可能擴大自己<br />\n農村包圍城市，司機包圍車主<br />\n依加target黃司機先都係一個方向丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"